                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>To Zeus. The people of the Segestans (have dedicated this statue of) Herakleios Pe[---] son of Nymphon, on account of his excellence</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" source="http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR">
                <p>A Zeus. Il popolo dei Segestani (ha onorator/ha eretto la statua di) Herakleios, figlio di Nymphon, Pe[---], per il suo valore [transl. from I.Segesta]</p>
            </div>
